RootCauseAnalysis - INFO -     Result: {'result': 'Looking at the trace analysis results, I can see significant latency anomalies in both Redis operations and CartService calls. Let me analyze the data:\n\nFrom the `trace_analysis_tool` results, I can see:\n1. **Redis HMSET operations** show severe latency issues:\n   - cartservice-1: normal avg 1,655μs → anomaly avg 18,605μs (11.2x increase)\n   - cartservice-2: normal avg 1,361μs → anomaly avg 13,792μs (10.1x increase)\n\n2. **CartService operations** also show significant latency increases:\n   - EmptyCart: normal avg 2,258-2,436μs → anomaly avg 19,552-42,239μs (8.6-18.7x increase)\n   - GetCart: normal avg 2,314μs → anomaly avg 8,265μs (3.6x increase)\n   - AddItem: normal avg 3,583-3,998μs → anomaly avg 18,304-20,293μs (4.5-5.7x increase)\n\nThe raw trace data from `search_raw_traces` shows that:\n- Redis HGET operations have durations ranging from 600-2094μs (relatively normal)\n- Redis HMSET operations appear to be the problematic ones\n- Frontend to CartService calls show client-side durations much higher than server-side durations, indicating the bottleneck is within the CartService itself, likely due to slow Redis operations\n\nThe pattern shows that CartService is experiencing increased latency when performing HMSET operations on Redis, which then causes cascading latency increases in all CartService operations (GetCart, AddItem, EmptyCart) that depend on Redis.\n\n```json\n{\n  "detected_trace_keys": ["rrt_max", "cartservice->redis", "HMSET", "frontend->cartservice"],\n  "affected_components": ["cartservice", "redis"],\n  "missing_traces": [],\n  "trace_summary": "Significant latency increase detected in Redis HMSET operations (10-11x normal duration) causing cascading latency in CartService operations. CartService GetCart, AddItem, and EmptyCart operations show 3.6-18.7x latency increases due to slow Redis HMSET operations.",\n  "next_verification": {\n    "action": "check_redis_performance",\n    "reason": "Redis HMSET operations show severe latency degradation which is the root cause of CartService performance issues",\n    "suggested_metrics": ["redis_cpu_usage", "redis_memory_usage", "redis_connections"],\n    "suggested_log_keywords": ["redis", "HMSET", "timeout", "slow"]\n  }\n}\n```'}
